# Operational KPI Reporting — IBM Cognos Analytics (DHL)

Data reporting and validation work from high-volume logistics operations at DHL.

## Overview
During my time at DHL Manchester (2023–2025), I built and maintained operational reports using IBM Cognos Analytics. Reports tracked shift throughput, data accuracy rates, and workflow efficiency across a high-volume logistics environment.

## Tools Used
- IBM Cognos Analytics 11
- Data validation workflows
- Excel (supporting analysis)

## Report Types Produced
| Report | Frequency | Key Metric |
|--------|-----------|------------|
| Shift Throughput | Daily | Units processed per shift |
| Accuracy Rate | Weekly | Data entry error rate |
| Workflow Efficiency | Weekly | Process bottleneck analysis |
| Discrepancy Log | Ad hoc | Flagged data anomalies |

## Key Outcomes
- Maintained **98.4% data accuracy** across reporting periods
- Identified recurring workflow bottlenecks leading to process improvements
- Standardised report templates adopted across the team

